<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Drone1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Drone,</orth> the male bee that makes no honey: <bibl n="shak. mv 2.5.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 5, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.204" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 204</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.109" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 109</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.0." default="NO" valid="yes">II Prol. 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 51</bibl>. Hence == a sluggard: <cit><quote>Dromio, thou d., thou snail,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 196</bibl></cit> (O. Edd. <emph>Dromio</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>